2bb900daacc1c9a1594fcc8516a0a5ab0345f609.query:
select
                    name as "name!",
                    caster as "caster!",
                    date_of_birth as "date_of_birth: NaiveDate",
                    timezone,
                    seven_tv_id,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                from channels
                where name = $1

a8a530b7fe6fd1c5060bcca7343481eb4bd1ced4.query:
select
                    id,
                    pattern,
                    case_insensitive,
                    expansion,
                    to_mention,
                    channel,
                    enabled,
                    created_by,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                from npc_replies
                where enabled = 1 and (channel is null or channel = $1)
                order by id asc

ba8935c9eca1044c537784c3d1f6933ec49917f6.query:
insert into npc_replies (pattern, expansion, channel, to_mention, enabled, created_by) values
            ("^!twitter$", $2, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!youtube$", $3, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!clips$", $4, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!vod(?:s)?(?:-)?(?:channel)?(?:s)?$", $5, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!reddit$", "reddit.com/r/PedroPeepos", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!discord$", $6, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!instagram$", $7, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!tiktok$", $8, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!social(?:s)?$", $9, "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("(?:^!stream$|\s*stream(?:ing)?\s+today\s*\?.*)$", "YEP Caedrel should be streaming today. Follow twitter.com/caedrelupdates for more updates", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("(?:^!cast$|\s*cast(?:ing)?\s+(?:lec\s+)?today(?:\?)?|\s*lec\s+(?:on\+s)?today(?:\?)?|\s*lec\s+on(?:\?)?)", "No LEC today Cryge You can find the schedule here lolesports.com/schedule?leagues=lec", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!end(?:ing)?(?:-)?song$", "okaywill - Chicken Dinner: youtube.com/watch?v=B_rAI7zaVZU", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),

            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:caedALLO|peepoSitHey|good\s+morning)(:?\s+)?.*", "caedALLO caedH", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:thanks|thank\s+you|thnx|ty)(?:\s+)?.*$", "ok", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:GIGACHAD|best\s+mod|good\s+mod|PETTHEMODS|<3|heart)(?:\s+)?.*", "caedH", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:bye)(?:\s+)?.*", "bye", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:Pog|PogU|POGGIES|POGGERS|caedPog)(?:\s+)?.*", "xddFlush", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:xdd.*)(?:\s+)?.*", "widexddL", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:Aware|TrollAware|TrollDespair|Despairge|xddDespair)(?:\s+)?.*", "Aware Despairge", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:DonoWall)(?:\s+)?.*", "classic DonoWall Despair", "caedrel", 1, 0, $1),

            ("^!emote(?:s)?$", "To see emotes install 7TV 7tv.app. These are `CASTER`'s emotes: 7tv.app/users/`SEVEN_TV_ID`", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!time$", "It's `NOW` in `CASTER`'s timezone", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!patch$", "Current patch in LCK & LPL is 13.5 ok", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!msi$", "MSI 2023 starts the 2nd of May PauseChamp", "caedrel", 0, 1, $1);
